Third-party notices (in-tree code derived from external projects):

The following portions of this repository contain or are derived from code
authored by third parties. The MIT grant above continues to apply to those
files as integrated here, and the upstream copyright notices are reproduced
below in satisfaction of the MIT attribution requirement.

  * `port/gui/Compat.h`, `port/gui/Menu.{cpp,h}`, `port/gui/MenuTypes.h`,
    `port/gui/PortMenu.{cpp,h}`, `port/gui/UIWidgets.{cpp,hpp}` —
    derived from the Ship of Harkinian (SoH) project.
      Copyright (c) The Harbour Masters
      https://github.com/HarbourMasters/Shipwright
      Licensed under the MIT License.

  * `port/audio/mixer.{c,h}`, and the watermark/buffering logic in
    `port/audio/audio_playback.cpp` — derived from the Starship (Star Fox 64)
    PC port.
      Copyright (c) The Harbour Masters
      https://github.com/HarbourMasters/Starship
      Licensed under the MIT License.

  * `port/renderdoc_app.h` — verbatim from the RenderDoc in-application API.
      Copyright (c) 2015-2026 Baldur Karlsson
      https://github.com/baldurk/renderdoc
      Licensed under the MIT License (notice retained in the file).

  * `gamecontrollerdb.txt` — community-maintained SDL game controller
    mappings.
      Source: https://github.com/mdqinc/SDL_GameControllerDB
      Licensed under the zlib License.
